              <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>my Situation</strong></p>
<p>I am a student of elearning &nbsp;pedagogy. I started my apprenticeship recently. I've realized that I have many difficulties and there are colleagues of mine who are much more advanced than me. I am aware of my limited knowledge.</p>
