          <pubDate>Sat, 12 Jan 2013 17:35:10 +0000</pubDate>
            </item>
                    <item>
              <title>Dreambazaar - oldsmooc - Helen Whitehead - e-assessment including of MOOCs</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/7113</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/7113</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>I'd like to do a project on e-assessment materials to support face tof ace and online courses, including MOOCs.</p>
<p><a href="http://helenwhitehead.com/blog2/2013/01/12/oldsmooc-dreambazaar-proposed-project/" target="_blank">More here</a></p>
