              <title>OLDS MOOC: getting started with cloudworks - step by step</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6664</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6664</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>You can find many more helpul resources in the&nbsp;<a href="http://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloudscape/view/1911">Using Cloudworks</a> cloudscape.</p>
